$$ = \pmatrix{ \frac{1}{2} + \frac{1}{3} + \frac{1}{6} & 0 + \frac{1}{3} - \frac{2}{6} & -\frac{1}{2} + \frac{1}{3} + \frac{1}{6} \\ 0 + \frac{1}{3} - \frac{2}{6} & 0 + \frac{1}{3} + \frac{4}{6} & 0 + \frac{1}{3} - \frac{2}{6} \\ -\frac{1}{2} + \frac{1}{3} + \frac{1}{6} & 0 + \frac{1}{3} - \frac{2}{6} & \frac{1}{2} + \frac{1}{3} + \frac{1}{6} } = \pmatrix{ 1 & 0 & 0 \\ 0 & 1 & 0 \\ 0 & 0 & 1 } = I$$

